Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.75,0:22:30.95,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\c&HE92EFD&\bord0}明けなくていいと　そう思ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.55,0:22:33.88,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\c&HE92EFD&\bord0}隠したい傷跡だって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.16,0:22:36.71,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\c&HE92EFD&\bord0}忘れたい記憶もみんな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.02,0:22:41.61,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\c&HE92EFD&\bord0}太陽は全部照らし出すから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.78,0:22:44.48,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\c&HE92EFD&\bord0}流星をさがし
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.21,0:22:47.00,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\c&HE92EFD&\bord0}彷徨ってたんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.85,0:22:54.84,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\c&HE92EFD&\bord0}あなたと出会う時まで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.30,0:23:01.85,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\c&HE92EFD&\bord0}空に瞬くあの星が
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.85,0:23:07.25,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\c&HE92EFD&\bord0}繋いだ希望の道の先へ行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.25,0:23:12.07,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\c&HE92EFD&\bord0}もう迷わずに進める
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.07,0:23:18.45,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\c&HE92EFD&\bord0}暗い夜を超える祈りを追いかけてく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.45,0:23:22.74,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\c&HE92EFD&\bord0}たとえまだ届かなくたって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.55,0:23:26.90,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\c&HE92EFD&\bord0}伝えたいから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.90,0:23:28.22,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\c&HE92EFD&\bord0}「ありがとう」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.66,0:22:26.75,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\c&HE92EFD&\bord0}都說太陽總會升起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.75,0:22:30.95,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\c&HE92EFD&\bord0}但不升起也挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.55,0:22:33.88,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\c&HE92EFD&\bord0}想隱藏的傷痕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.16,0:22:36.71,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\c&HE92EFD&\bord0}想忘卻的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.02,0:22:41.61,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\c&HE92EFD&\bord0}會被太陽照得一清二楚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.78,0:22:44.48,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\c&HE92EFD&\bord0}尋找著流星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.21,0:22:47.00,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\c&HE92EFD&\bord0}獨自彷徨著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.85,0:22:54.84,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\c&HE92EFD&\bord0}直到與你相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.30,0:23:01.85,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\c&HE92EFD&\bord0}在天空閃爍的那顆星
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.85,0:23:07.25,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\c&HE92EFD&\bord0}照亮了希望之路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.25,0:23:12.07,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\c&HE92EFD&\bord0}不再迷茫 徑直向前
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.07,0:23:18.45,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\c&HE92EFD&\bord0}跨過漆黑的夜晚 追隨著祈願
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.45,0:23:22.74,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\c&HE92EFD&\bord0}即使還傳達不到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.55,0:23:26.90,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\c&HE92EFD&\bord0}也想說一聲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.90,0:23:28.22,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\c&HE92EFD&\bord0}「謝謝」
